question:
What will be the output of the following code snippet?

```java
public class Test {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println(mystery(3));
    }
    public static int mystery(int n) {
        if (n == 0) {
            return 1;
        } else {
            return n * mystery(n - 1);
        }
    }
}
```
